{"id": "work_cd47d6df-7c35-549f-992a-2203b480498f", "title": "Extending the lifetime of a quantum bit with error correction in superconducting circuits", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1015941993"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:33.199143", "abstract": "A quantum-error-correction system is demonstrated in which natural errors due to energy loss are suppressed by encoding a logical state as a superposition of Schr\u00f6dinger-cat states, which results in the system reaching the \u2018break-even\u2019 point, at which the lifetime of a qubit exceeds the lifetime of the constituents of the system.", "publication_date": "2016-07-20", "doi": "10.1038/nature18949", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1015941993?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_29ddf23f-0a4d-5b49-b670-16f2b7f1087b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_76cadbe7-fd88-507e-9d7e-a022740d6f63", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d0bebc3a-241c-5991-8f55-be42bd6cb0d6", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_c92a2af3-2e7f-504f-9ac1-e9889e40832e", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_ae81ab3d-0ed0-5005-a21f-7ddc960765df", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_8d6a024e-9c10-578a-bb58-85bde55a929c", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_e91a6c7b-e8b9-50ef-92e2-eab4745cb20c", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_bac6dc31-4282-50fc-88c6-f4f33716c410", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id"